The following are the national records in [[Olympic weightlifting]] in the [[Solomon Islands]]. Records are maintained in each [[weight class]] for the [[snatch (weightlifting)|snatch]] lift, [[clean and jerk]] lift, and the total for both lifts by the [[Solomon Islands Weightlifting Federation]].
